Dafne Keen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dafne_Keen 0 Dafne Keen Fernández (born 2005) is a British and Spanish actress who played the role of Ana "Ani" Cruz Oliver in the television series The Refugees, and the mutant Laura Kinney / X-23 in the 2017 film Logan.
